body:
@wzzju : The command that you specified is building a java library, is that correct?

For benchmarks the command looks correct, the only thing I may change would be to use config=android_arm64 for 64 bit.

We have published a few performance numbers on our [website](https://www.tensorflow.org/mobile/tflite/performance): 
 for some common models. Some of the numbers are also listed [here](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/tensorflow/contrib/lite/g3doc/models.md).
